37
00:03:28,978 --> 00:03:34,778
"The House of Death, Red Wall (Empty Fort Strategy)"

38
00:03:37,078 --> 00:03:38,678
I see.

39
00:03:38,678 --> 00:03:41,478
That's why the chairs of the first murder site

40
00:03:41,478 --> 00:03:44,478
were painted black and white.

41
00:03:44,478 --> 00:03:45,678
Yep!

42
00:03:45,678 --> 00:03:48,778
It seemed that the victim, Mr. Akashi

43
00:03:48,778 --> 00:03:51,578
liked chess too!

44
00:03:51,578 --> 00:03:53,878
If so, why did the culprit

45
00:03:53,878 --> 00:03:57,678
paint the wall of the second murder red?

46
