79
00:05:28,378 --> 00:05:32,378
Just like Koume and Zhou did before the Battle of Red Cliffs!

80
00:05:34,678 --> 00:05:35,678
All right.

81
00:05:35,678 --> 00:05:37,878
Geez, what a hassle.

82
00:05:42,178 --> 00:05:43,278
Here goes.

83
00:05:43,278 --> 00:05:45,178
Ready, get set.

84
00:05:49,678 --> 00:05:51,878
Just as I thought after all.

85
00:05:51,878 --> 00:05:54,378
The Empty Fort Strategy!

86
00:05:54,378 --> 00:05:56,378
"Empty."

87
