96
00:06:22,478 --> 00:06:26,278
In the first place, did you solve the mystery of the red wall?

97
00:06:26,278 --> 00:06:29,278
We haven't solved that mystery yet.

98
00:06:29,278 --> 00:06:33,278
But, it seems that Mr. Shiro Naoki who became the second victim,

99
00:06:33,278 --> 00:06:35,878
have caught on to something.

100
00:06:35,878 --> 00:06:37,678
Do you have any idea what it could be?

101
00:06:37,678 --> 00:06:39,278
I wonder.

102
00:06:39,278 --> 00:06:42,178
