106
00:06:52,978 --> 00:06:54,878
to the place called Lecce

107
00:06:54,878 --> 00:06:58,078
to hide something important!

108
00:06:58,078 --> 00:07:00,778
Besides, it seems that he also said

109
00:07:00,778 --> 00:07:03,978
to come to look for him there after he's gone.

110
00:07:03,978 --> 00:07:06,078
