111
00:07:06,078 --> 00:07:09,578
Because Italy is shaped like a shoe, isn't it?

112
00:07:09,578 --> 00:07:11,678
At any rate!

113
00:07:11,678 --> 00:07:14,778
If you want to investigate us any further...

114
00:07:14,778 --> 00:07:18,178
Do that after you find necessary proof.

115
00:07:18,178 --> 00:07:20,778
We don't have all the time in the world too, you see.

116
00:07:20,778 --> 00:07:22,378
See you.

117
00:07:22,378 --> 00:07:23,678
If you will excuse me then.

118
00:07:27,478 --> 00:07:29,878
We've done what needs to be done,

119
00:07:29,878 --> 00:07:33,378
so now we sit and wait, right?

120
00:07:33,378 --> 00:07:34,778
Those who travel a 100 miles

121
00:07:34,778 --> 00:07:37,078
regard 90 miles as only half.

122
00:07:37,078 --> 00:07:39,178
We should keep on our guard.

123
00:07:39,178 --> 00:07:40,778
Yeah.

124
00:07:40,778 --> 00:07:43,778
We can't afford not solving this case, after we've come this far.

125
00:07:51,078 --> 00:07:53,278
PC60, PC60.

126
00:07:53,278 --> 00:07:55,278
A taxi robbery occurred in the industry area...

127
00:07:55,278 --> 00:07:57,878
Darn. Just as I thought,

128
00:07:57,878 --> 00:08:01,178
