129
00:08:01,178 --> 00:08:03,678
So, it was a trap after all.

130
00:08:03,678 --> 00:08:06,078
What? A taxi robbery?

131
00:08:06,078 --> 00:08:07,178
Near here?

132
00:08:07,178 --> 00:08:09,678
Yeah, they want us there on the double.

133
00:08:14,678 --> 00:08:17,678
What happened? Are they going to leave?

134
00:08:17,678 --> 00:08:20,578
Which means that, this apartment is going to be empty.

135
00:08:26,578 --> 00:08:28,278
No, wait.

136
00:08:28,278 --> 00:08:31,278
The drunkard that fell forward in front of the apartment just now

137
00:08:31,278 --> 00:08:32,278
and the man wearing the mask

138
00:08:32,278 --> 00:08:34,578
