140
00:08:38,278 --> 00:08:43,278
Sir, you'll catch cold sleeping in a place like this!

141
00:08:43,278 --> 00:08:46,178
Shut up! Stay out of this!

142
00:08:46,178 --> 00:08:49,278
Idiot! Who gives a hoot about the chairman...

143
00:08:50,778 --> 00:08:52,578
I guess the drunkard's not an officer.

144
00:08:52,578 --> 00:08:55,078
Hey, you. Are you all right?

145
00:08:55,078 --> 00:08:57,278
You're so drunk.

146
00:08:58,878 --> 00:09:02,178
I can go another two or three shops!

147
00:09:03,478 --> 00:09:04,678
Hey!

148
00:09:04,678 --> 00:09:06,278
Oh, I'm sorry.

149
00:09:06,278 --> 00:09:11,378
I broke my leg!

150
00:09:11,378 --> 00:09:13,978
Are you all right?

151
00:09:14,978 --> 00:09:16,278
Hey, jerk!

152
00:09:16,278 --> 00:09:18,678
Give me a million yen to pay for what you did!

153
00:09:18,678 --> 00:09:20,578
1 million yen?

154
00:09:20,578 --> 00:09:22,778
I don't have that much money!

155
00:09:22,778 --> 00:09:25,278
Then, give me your wallet and all!

156
00:09:25,278 --> 00:09:26,478
No!

157
00:09:26,478 --> 00:09:28,178
