192
00:11:52,072 --> 00:11:54,172
Conan Edogawa.

193
00:11:54,172 --> 00:11:55,572
A detective.

194
00:11:55,572 --> 00:11:57,872
It's you?

195
00:11:58,564 --> 00:12:00,264
