196
00:12:00,264 --> 00:12:01,964
You...

197
00:12:01,964 --> 00:12:03,464
Haven't forgotten...

198
00:12:03,464 --> 00:12:04,964
Us!

199
00:12:04,964 --> 00:12:06,464
Then the mugging

200
00:12:06,464 --> 00:12:08,364
and thief breaking in that I saw a while ago were...

